nodes.title: Trade Order hierarchy for wallet_exchange_convert
nodes.body: An order can have multiple trades associated with it Create a hierarchy in the database and support in API, Scheduler View to return a summary and another view to display details about trades in the order The procedure should support this by looking up by order to see if an order exists and match appropriately - [ ] SQL Table - [ ] SQL View Flattened - [ ] SQL View Summary (order) - [ ] SQL View Detail (trades in order) - [ ] SQL Procedure - [ ] Scheduler Import - [ ] API
